queries.sql: SELECT `a`.*, `p`.`first_name` as `patient_first_name`, `p`.`last_name` as `patient_last_name`, `p`.`phone` as `patient_phone`, `u`.`username` as `doctor_name`, `u`.`email` as `doctor_email` FROM `appointments` `a` LEFT JOIN `patients` `p` ON `a`.`patient_id` = `p`.`id` LEFT JOIN `users` `u` ON `a`.`doctor_id` = `u`.`id` LEFT JOIN `roles` `r` ON `u`.`role_id` = `r`.`id` WHERE `r`.`name` = 'doctor' ORDER BY FIELD(a.status, 'scheduled','confirmed','in_progress','completed','cancelled','no_show') ASC, FIELD(a.status, 'scheduled','confirmed','in_progress','completed','cancelled','no_show') ASC, `a`.`appointment_date` ASC, `a`.`appointment_time` ASC
